Package data

package data
The data package provides classes for data storage and save/load operations. It includes classes designed to handle the storage and retrieval of data within an application.

The main classes in this package are:

  • DataStorage - Manages the storage of data within the application.
  • SaveLoad - Facilitates the save and load operations for application data.

DataStorage provides methods for storing and retrieving data in a structured manner. It serves as a central component for managing the application's data storage requirements.

SaveLoad is responsible for handling the saving and loading of application data. It provides methods to save the current state of the application and load data from a previously saved state.

Each class in this package plays a crucial role in managing the data aspects of the application. For detailed information about each class, refer to their respective documentation.
